quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,5,"Abo babula obumanyi bwosibwosi bwalio, kata baasabwe bosi. Ni likhuwa likhongo muno lirulanga muminwa chiabu. Shibaboolanga halali obubeyi butswa."
  18,6,"Ne onyala okhwiyira ewe omwene khulwa okhubabelelela ngala bali mbu shibasubilanga amakhuwa kano tawe."
  18,7,"Toto efwe khwakhola ebili khushialo bibe ebirone biashio, kho khubateme ni wina mubo webikhole ebilayi muno."
  18,8,"Ne toto nefwe khulikhola bioosi ebo bili hekulu walio okhuba liloba eliumu."
  18,9,"Nohomba oparanga mbu Abandu ba mumbinga nende kalia kahandikwa, mbu biali ebiamakana okhurulana nende ebimanyisio biefu?"
  18,10,"Olwa Abasiani abo belushila mumbinga, mana nibaboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khuhelesie tsimbabaasi tsirulanga khwiwe ne khukasilie obulunjifu mulikhuwa liefu.”"
  18,11,"Mana nikhusuba amarwi kabu mumbinga omo khumika eminji."
  18,12,"Mana nikhubalamusia khokhumanye mbu kuli hena khumikanda chibili chino okwabala obulayi muno ebise biabamenya."
  18,13,"Efwe khukhukanilanga amakhuwa kabu khubwatoto. Toto abo ni ababuukha, abasuubila Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, mana nikhubametela obulunjifu."
  18,14,"Mana nikhura amaani mumioyo chiabu olwabeema mana nibaboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi ni Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, shikhulalaamakhwo Nyasaye wundi yesiyesi ulali Ye tawe. Toto awo khulaba khuboolele obubii obwaburirira eshichelo."
  18,15,"Abandu befu bano bakhola abanyasaye balali Ye tawe. Shichila shina nibalarerakhwo eshifune shili habulafu? Kho ni omubii shina omukhongo muno okhushila ulia uchishilanga Nyasaye obubeyi?""